         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">21/10/91 ¶  ¶ The Duboisia, sent by you, dear Mr Gill, is the D. Hopwoodii, which differs from D. myoporoides in much narrower leaves and in some other respects; it is also of other geographic distibu...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">91.10.21</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Walter Gill</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M33, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21/10/91</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Duboisia, sent by you, dear Mr Gill, is the D. Hopwoodii, which differs from D. myoporoides in much narrower leaves and in some other respects; it is also of other geographic distibution, D. myoporoides belonging to humid forest regions of litoral tracts only.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As the medicinal properties are much like those of <name key="Hyoscyamus">Hyoscyamus</name> and <name key="Belladonna">Belladonna</name>, it is a highly dangerous plant. I should like to have some ripe berries, so that I could rear this species for therapeutic experiments freshly in some quantity</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Eucalyptus, of which you sent a branchlet in fruit, is not Euc. Leucoxylon. Could you procure also flowering specimens?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
